title: Parmesan-Crumbed Pork Schnitzel with Celery Slaw & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: It's easy to whip up a classic pork schnitzel at home, and we're going to show you how! Make it a meal with a crunchy, tangy slaw, studded with almonds and celery, plus some pesto dressing for dipping. Delicious!

